{"tid":1199504,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"〔概念𨤳清〕通過修例並不代表抗爭完結！！！！！！！","createTime":"2019-06-10T13:35:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T06:27:06.000Z","uid":32906,"like":110,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"58cc14dfd62c7d758c34cd6189e5437dde2ff477","tid":1199504,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:35:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大眾都認為通過修例就等於人民輸了抗爭結束<br />\n<br />\n其實大錯特錯<br />\n<br />\n抗爭就係要直到修例消失！！！<br />\n<br />\n唔理11號12號定13號<br />\n<br />\n我地要話比所有人聽<br />\n<br />\n有送中就有我地<br />\n<br />\n我地要堅持到最後<br />\n<br />\n大家概念要清晰<br />\n<br />\n唔好再信通過等於玩完<br />\n<br />\n如果狗官知道通過修例後我地就會死死氣番屋企<br />\n<br />\n咁敵人仲洗理我地既？？！！！！<br />\n<br />\n總之。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不撒不散</span></span></span></span>"},{"pid":"970be0377e802c9008ac6dcceff27b41387fdecd","tid":1199504,"uid":32906,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:43:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">另外各派人士應該互相尊重<br />\n各有各做<br />\n但所有行動衡需要組織和溝通<br />\n單獨行動只會自取滅亡<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"336e83ef73e177b39c8c257c552fdd15f5394f9c","tid":1199504,"uid":32906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:51:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1198000/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1198000/page/1</a><br />\n有位熱心巴打開帖，此帖正評過千。<br />\n但因為概念有錯所以必須提醒大家。"},{"pid":"a761f169876f032dcdf2ba53a6062cb966f0e4da","tid":1199504,"uid":131122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:55:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f4a9e34159b849dca0799648b664f73caef5d658","tid":1199504,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:55:38.000Z","msg":"條例通過就要目送狗官番屋企<br />\n唔係咁好呀麻！！"},{"pid":"6f6fc6f51cf278a5dcbb941440ad56c8d05d7e28","tid":1199504,"uid":32906,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:03:17.000Z","msg"